@section EventsHeader {
    <div class="mb-4" id="backend-error-container"></div>
}

<noscript>
    <div class="alert alert-header mt-5" role="alert">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="alert-heading">Your browser does not support JavaScript.</h4>
            <span class="separator"></span>
            <p class="mb-0">
                For full functionality of this website it is necessary to enable JavaScript.<br />
                Here are the <a href="https://www.enable-javascript.com/">instructions how to enable it in your web browser</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</noscript>

<div class="alert alert-secondary text-center alert-report" role="alert">
    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> If a service isn't working for you, click on the exclamation mark to share your reporting. A significant number of reports may indicate an issue with game servers. Keep in mind that Hitman's services also rely on Azure's infrastructure and third-party digital distribution  platforms services. If Hitman's servers appear online here but you still have some issues, you can check <a href="https://steamstat.us/">Steam status</a>, <a href="https://status.playstation.com/">PSN status</a>, <a href="https://support.xbox.com/en-US/xbox-live-status">Xbox Live status</a> and <a href="https://status.azure.com/">Azure status</a> websites to get more informations.
</div>

@Html.AntiForgeryToken()

<div id="services-container"></div>

<h4 class="index-title mb-4">
    <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
    Down reported last week
    <small class="text-muted">(by community players)</small>
</h4>

<div class="mb-5" id="chart"></div>

@section Scripts {
    <script src="~/js/scripts.min.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
}